 Bobertron took in the information in great lengths. He knew all about the 
ship. Hidden compatrments and hidden findings he did not know of before. Now 
all he had to do was wait for the upload to be complete. Now he knew that if 
Magmatron was a smart leader he would not show him all of the ships hidden 
secrets until his demise. So he tried to search for a block of some kind. 
Suddenly a shock came through his body. Not much damage was done to him but 
it smarted. Suddenly he heard Magmatron's voice, "Now you should have 
expected a safe guard like this. Now complete your uplink and start your 
leadership."
